<p>
  <span class="nym">Erma</span>
  <span class="gen">f.</span>
  
  <span class="etym">A pet form of any of various names beginning with <span class="lang">Old High German</span> <i>ermen</i>, <span class="lang">Old Saxon</span> <i>irmin</i> 'strong', such as <a class="nym" href="Ermenburg">Ermenburg</a>, <a class="nym" href="Ermentrude">Ermentrude</a>, or <a class="nym" href="Ermengard">Ermengard</a>, or the same element used as a standalone name.
</span>
  
</p>
  
  
  


